summary: Natives of planet Vegeta the Saiyans are not from Nirn, and are actually space pirates, they conquer planets and sell them on the Galactic Market, you were sent to Nirn in a space pod to conquer it for the Saiyans.
descriptionHtml:
[i]Natives of planet Vegeta the Saiyans are not from Nirn, and are actually space pirates, they conquer planets and sell them on the Galactic Market, you were sent to Nirn in a space pod to conquer it for the Saiyans.

[/i]Features:
[list=1]
[*][i]New Saiyan race, mainly Nord features with Khajiit tail.[/i]
[*][i]4 new destruction spells, bought from Farengar.[/i]
[*][i]New racial ability, Saiyan Strength, basically the same as claws[/i]
[/list]
author: Kris6464
